item.title: CVE-2023-32470|2024-08-02T15:18:37.194Z -- dell -- dell%20digital%20delivery
item.description: Dell Digital Delivery versions prior to 5.0.82.0 contain an Insecure Operation on Windows Junction / Mount Point vulnerability. A local malicious user could potentially exploit this vulnerability to create arbitrary folder leading to permanent Denial of Service (DOS).
